   "source": [
    "# 🧾 Doc Agent — Multi-Modal Document Intelligence\n",
    "### Capstone Project | AI-Powered Invoice & Form Processing\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 📌 What is this project?\n",
    "\n",
    "**Doc Agent** is a LangGraph-based multi-agent AI system that automatically reads invoices, receipts, and forms — extracting structured data, validating it, auto-correcting errors, and flagging uncertain documents for human review.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Architecture (Block Diagram)\n",
    "```\n",
    "┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n",
    "│  INPUT: PDF · PNG · JPG · TIFF · Scanned Image              │\n",
    "└──────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────┘\n",
    "                           ▼\n",
    "┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n",
    "│  INGESTION PIPELINE                                          │\n",
    "│  pdf2image (300 DPI) → Pillow deskew → Contrast enhance     │\n",
    "└──────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────┘\n",
    "                           ▼\n",
    "┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n",
    "│  CLASSIFICATION AGENT  (Gemini Vision)                       │\n",
    "│  Invoice / Receipt / Form  →  selects extraction schema     │\n",
    "└──────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────┘\n",
    "                           ▼\n",
    "┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n",
    "│  EXTRACTION AGENT  (Gemini Vision)                           │\n",
    "│  Structured prompt → Pydantic object                         │\n",
    "│  Fields: invoice_number, vendor, date, items, tax, total     │\n",
    "│       ↓ low confidence?                                      │\n",
    "│  OCR FALLBACK (Tesseract) → merge with VLM output            │\n",
    "└──────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────┘\n",
    "                           ▼\n",
    "┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n",
    "│  VALIDATION AGENT                                            │\n",
    "│  Rule-based: total = subtotal+tax | date ISO | IBAN format   │\n",
    "│  Semantic:   vendor name → ChromaDB + rapidfuzz matching     │\n",
    "│       ↓ fail?                                                │\n",
    "│  AUTO-CORRECTION AGENT → crop region → re-query VLM         │\n",
    "│       ↓ still fail after 2 attempts?                         │\n",
    "│  HUMAN REVIEW QUEUE (UI)                                     │\n",
    "└──────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────┘\n",
    "                           ▼\n",
    "┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n",
    "│  SQLITE STORAGE  +  JSON / CSV Export                        │\n",
    "│  Audit trail: every step logged                              │\n",
    "└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## ✅ Prerequisites — What You Need\n",
    "\n",
    "| Requirement | Details | Cost |\n",
    "|-------------|---------|------|\n",
    "| Google Account | For Colab + Gemini API | **Free** |\n",
    "| Gemini API Key | See Step 2 below | **Free** |\n",
    "| GPU | Not required — Gemini runs in the cloud | — |\n",
    "| Python packages | Auto-installed in Step 1 | — |\n",
    "| Tesseract OCR | Auto-installed in Step 1 | — |\n",
    "\n",
    "> 💡 **No paid subscriptions needed.** This project uses Google Gemini's free tier which gives you 1,500 requests/day — more than enough for a capstone project.\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 🔑 Step 2 Preview — How to get your free Gemini API Key\n",
    "\n",
    "1. Go to **https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey**\n",
    "2. Sign in with your Google account (same one you use for Colab)\n",
    "3. Click **\"Create API key\"** → **\"Create API key in new project\"**\n",
    "4. Copy the key (starts with `AIza...`)\n",
    "5. Paste it in **Step 2** below\n",
    "\n",
    "That's it — takes about 2 minutes.\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## ⚡ Quick Start (3 steps)\n",
