    "| **`pdf2image` error on PDF** | Re-run Step 1a to install `poppler-utils` |\n",
    "| **Colab session expired** | Re-run ALL cells from Step 1 (sessions reset every ~12h on free tier) |\n",
    "| **App URL expired** | Re-run Step 4 to get a new tunnel URL |\n",
    "| **Login not working** | Credentials are `demo` / `demo` (hardcoded in `ui/auth.py`) |\n",
